{
  "chapter": 62,
  "chapter_summary": "小鱼儿追上花无缺马车，提出三月之约：三月后在武汉一决生死，期间互不干涉。花无缺应允。二人离去后，铁心兰向花无缺坦白对小鱼儿的感情，花无缺深感痛苦却隐忍不发。此时一神秘穷汉现身，看出花无缺移花宫门人身份，竟要强行逼婚。花无缺宁死不从，铁心兰情急之下答应成亲，花无缺仍断然拒绝。穷汉出手试探，花无缺使出移花接玉，却被穷汉轻易化解。穷汉见花无缺不姓江，转身欲去，花无缺怒而反击。穷汉自报身份——正是与移花宫仇深如海的燕南天，十年磨剑只为将移花宫门人杀尽杀绝。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "花无缺慢走！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你以为我是送死来的，是么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你既然这么想杀我，为何不来找我却等我来找你？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我自己本不愿杀你，所以也并未急着找你，但此刻我既然见着你，却还是非杀你不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "这次是他自己来找你的，至少这次你不能杀他。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你为什么这样对我？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "这铁姑娘听说是你未过门的妻子，为何来管我闲事，我根本连认都不认得她。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这次你不要别人帮忙了么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我若要人帮忙，为何来找你？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你心里自然也知道，我这种人，是绝不会为了送死而来找你的，那么，我是为何而来的，你心里必定又在奇怪。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "正是有些奇怪。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你以为我杀不死你，我也以为你杀不死我，若是这样拖下去，拖到两百年后也不知究竟是你对，还是我对，我心里着急，你只怕比我更急。所以，我今天来，正是为了要和你做个了断！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你想如何来做了断？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你只要说个地方，三个月后，我必定去找你一决生死！没有分出生死强弱前，谁也不许逃走！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "但在这三个月的约期未到之前，你纵然瞧见了我，也得装着没有瞧见，更不能来寻我动手！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我若不来找你，这三个月，你反正是找不着我的，这条件你并没有吃亏，你为何不肯答应？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你说出这条件，其中想必又有诡计。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你……你不答应？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "三个月后，我在武汉一带，你必定可以找到我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "很好，你如此信任我，我必定不会使你失望！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你明知那其中必有诡计，为何还要答应他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你为何不说话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "沉默，有时岂非比说什么话都好？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "这两年来，你处处照顾着我，若不是你，我早已死了，我这一辈子，从来也没有人像你对我这么好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我这一生中，也从没有人像他对我那么坏，但是我……我也不知为了什么，一瞧见他，就没了主意。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "这些话，你本来不必对我说的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我也知道这话不该说的，但若不对你说个明白，我心里更难受，更觉得对不起你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "这怎能怪你？你又有什么对我不起？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "年纪轻轻，为了这种小事就痛苦不堪，等你们长大了，就会知道世上比这种更痛苦千万倍的事，还多着哩！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "莫非就是他？否则怎会如此相像，别人的事我可不管，但是他……我岂能不成全他的心意。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你心里可是很喜欢这位姑娘？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "这……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "什么沉默比说话好，全是狗屁，你不说出来，人家怎知你喜欢她。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "有些话，他不必说，我也知道。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "很好，不想你竟比他痛快得多，这样的女孩子，莫说是他，就连我见了，都有些喜欢。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你喜不喜欢他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "我不……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "我也不是不喜欢，只是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "既然不是不喜欢，自然是喜欢了。你两人既然彼此喜欢，就由我来作媒，今日就在这里成了亲吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "阁下莫非在开玩笑么！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "这怎会是开玩笑？你瞧此地，鸟语花香，风和日丽，你两人在这里成亲，岂非比什么地方都好得多？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "红烛之光，又怎及阳光之美。世上所有的红毡，更都不比这泥土芬芳柔软，你两人就在这阳光下、泥土上，快快拜了天地，岂非人生一大乐事，就连我都觉得痛快已极！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "阁下虽是一番好意，怎奈我等却绝难从命。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你不答应？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我知道了，这不是你不愿意，只是你怕她不愿意。但她既未说话，你又何苦多心。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "有许多话，是不必说出来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你明明喜欢她喜欢得要命，但为了她，却宁可硬着心肠不答应，这样的多情种子，倒真不愧是你爹爹的儿子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "像这样的男人，你不嫁给他嫁给谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "在下什么人都见过，倒真还没有见过如此逼人成亲的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你如此说话，想必是以为我宰不了你，是么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "我答应了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "我绝不答应。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "她都答应了，你为何不答应？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "我不答应，就是不答应，你若要杀我，只管动手就是！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你……你难道不喜欢我？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你宁可终生痛苦，也不答应？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "绝不答应。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "好！我与其让你终生受苦，倒不如现在就宰了你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "前辈快请住手，他不肯答应只是为了我，我心里才真是不肯答应的，前辈你要杀，就杀了我吧！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "姓江的果然都是牛一般的脾气，只是你却比你爹爹还呆。试想她若真的不肯答应你，真的不喜欢你，又怎肯为你死？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "他自然不姓江，他叫花无缺。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你不姓江？这倒真的是件怪事，你简直彻头彻尾像个姓江的，你简直和他长得一模一样。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你既然不姓江，成不成亲，就全都不关我的事了，你要走就走吧。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这少年居然不是江小鱼，奇怪奇怪……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "前辈莫非以为他是江小鱼，才逼着我们成亲的么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我虽然是不忍见着你们为情受苦，但若非认定他是江小鱼，我实在也不会多管闲事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我明白了，我明白了！原来你说的那对你最坏的人，就是江小鱼，你两人本来是会成亲的，就为了江小鱼，才弄成这般模样。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本来想成人好事，谁知却将这件事越弄越糟了……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "你就想走了么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我知道你心里不舒服，就让你打两拳出出气吧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "你武功纵然强绝天下，却也万万受不了我一掌，你若不招架，可是自寻死路！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "果然好掌力！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "你究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我一生总以未能一试移花宫武功为恨，不想今日竟在此地遇见了移花宫门下……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "前辈莫非与移花宫有什么过不去么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiong_han",
      "speaker_name": "穷汉",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我正是与移花宫仇深如海，我十年磨剑，为的正是要将移花宫门下，杀尽杀绝！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_qiong_han",
      "text": "燕南天！你是燕南天！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    }
